The paper deals with the security of compressed sensing measurements of natural images, which falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR) sub-categories. The paper also involves image processing (cs.MM, cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques for the proposed joint quantization and diffusion approach.
